COMMAND: kb <monster> (killing blow)
COST: NONE
DURATION: N/A
LEVEL: 12

Issue a killing blow to a weakened monster.
The monster must be below at least 20% their max hit points AND below
the maximum amount of damage you can inflict, which is based on your
strength, level, and the quality of your weapon.

You MUST have a weapon to use this command.

